{"type":"answer","id":56144,"parentType":"question","parentId":12940,"uid":8437,"contents":"正想发这个，被你抢先了。我先补上图：<br>\n<a href=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EkjJV_KVgAEsbtS?format=jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EkjJV_KVgAEsbtS?format=jpg\" alt=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EkjJV_KVgAEsbtS?format=jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<hr><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EkkKtV6UcAAMhJN?format=jpg&amp;name=small\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EkkKtV6UcAAMhJN?format=jpg&amp;name=small\" alt=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EkkKtV6UcAAMhJN?format=jpg&amp;name=small\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<hr><br>\n<br>\n<ul><li>不要给我光明</li><li>光明姓党，请习检阅</li></ul><br>\n<ul><li>黑暗牛奶（不过我估计没人买了以后）</li></ul><br>\nby@moses20160512[url=https://twitter.com/Moses20160512][/url]<br>\n<ul><li>“吃奶莫忘产奶人，光明不忘习主席”</li><li>&nbsp;“金山上升起不落的光明，习主席就是那金色的太阳” </li><li>“梁家河水清凌凌，光明牛奶白花花”</li></ul><br>\n<hr><br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<b>嗦嗦我对此事的看法：<br>\n<br>\n</b>1.中共居然文字狱到这个地步，<b>它到底多害怕啊</b>？<br>\n2.光明这波不知道是真<b>冲塔</b>还是不小心踩线了，前者：真英雄；后者：真不小心。<br>\n3.三十万，对他们来说应该不算太疼，还好。<br>\n4<b>.</b>中共所谓的”国家尊严“就值30万？<br>\n5.这波啊，光明一举成名，不亏。30万算是在海内外打了两次广告。<b>习亡</b>人没事。<br>\n<br>\n<hr><br>\n修宪一：<br>\n<br>\n<b>恰恰</b>和<b>光明</b>这是约好了一起冲塔？？？？<br>\n第二波来啦！！！<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EkkzWG9WMAAeIpQ?format=jpg&amp;name=large\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EkkzWG9WMAAeIpQ?format=jpg&amp;name=large\" alt=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EkkzWG9WMAAeIpQ?format=jpg&amp;name=large\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n官方说“自由”，那是宣传社会主义核心价值观，是正能量； 老百姓举个牌子要“自由”，那叫寻衅滋事。","date":"2020-10-18","agreeCount":12,"discussionCount":0}